section.def:
Board
                (管理局) means the Board of Governors of the
            Hospital established by section 4;

Chairman
                (主席) means the Chairman of the Board appointed
            under section 5(1) or (4);

Comptroller
                (審計主任) means the Comptroller of the Hospital
            appointed under section 12(3);

Hospital
                (醫院) means The Prince Philip Dental
            Hospital;
